317,351,371,374,398,399,411,416]},"species":"muk","gen":"generation-i","leg":false,"myth":false,"baby":false,"eggs":["Amorphous"],"flavor":[{"version":"red","text":"Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. It is so toxic, even its footprints contain poison."},{"version":"blue","text":"Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. It is so toxic, even its footprints contain poison."},{"version":"yellow","text":"Smells so awful, it can cause fainting. Through degeneration, it lost its sense of smell."},{"version":"gold","text":"They love to gath\u00ad er in smelly areas where sludge ac\u00ad cumulates, making the stench around them worse."},{"version":"silver","text":"Its body is made of a powerful poi\u00ad son. Touching it accidentally will cause a fever that requires bed rest."},{"version":"crystal","text":"As it moves, a very strong poison leaks from it, making the ground there barren for three years."},{"version":"ruby","text":"From MUK\u2019s body seeps a foul fluid that gives off a nose-bendingly horrible stench. Just one drop of this POK\u00e9MON\u2019s body fluid can turn a pool stagnant and rancid."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"This POK\u00e9MON\u2019s favorite food is anything that is repugnantly filthy. In dirty towns where people think nothing of throwing away litter on the streets, MUK are certain to gather."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It prefers warm and humid habitats. In the summertime, the toxic substances in its body intensify, making MUK reek like putrid kitchen garbage."},{"version":"firered","text":"It is usually undetectable because it blends in with the ground. Touching it can cause terrible poisoning."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. It is so toxic, even its footprints contain poison."},{"version":"diamond","text":"A toxic fluid seeps from its body. The fluid instantly kills plants and trees on contact."},{"version":"pearl","text":"A toxic fluid seeps from its body. The fluid instantly kills plants and trees on contact."},{"version":"platinum","text":"A toxic fluid seeps from its body. The fluid instantly kills plants and trees on contact."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"They love to gather in smelly areas where sludge accumulates, making the stench around them worse."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its body is made of a powerful poison. Touching it accidentally will cause a fever that requires bed rest."},{"version":"black","text":"A toxic fluid seeps from its body. The fluid instantly kills plants and trees on contact."},{"version":"white","text":"A toxic fluid seeps from its body. The fluid instantly kills plants and trees on contact."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It\u2019s so stinky! Muk\u2019s body contains toxic elements, and any plant will wilt when it passes by."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It\u2019s so stinky! Muk\u2019s body contains toxic elements, and any plant will wilt when it passes by."},{"version":"x","text":"They love to gather in smelly areas where sludge accumulates, making the stench around them worse."},{"version":"y","text":"A toxic fluid seeps from its body. The fluid instantly kills plants and trees on contact."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"From Muk\u2019s body seeps a foul fluid that gives off a nose-bendingly horrible stench. Just one drop of this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s body fluid can turn a pool stagnant and rancid."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s favorite food is anything that is repugnantly filthy. In dirty towns where people think nothing of throwing away litter on the streets, Muk are certain to gather."},{"version":"sun","text":"The stench it gives off will make your nose scrunch up. Still, there are Muk fans who think that\u2019s a good thing."},{"version":"moon","text":"After recent environmental improvements, this Pok\u00e9mon is now hardly seen at all. People speculate that it may go extinct at some point."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Their food sources have decreased, and their numbers have declined sharply. Sludge ponds are being built to prevent their extinction."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Because they scatter germs everywhere, they\u2019ve long been targeted for extermination, leading to a steep decline in their population."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Smells so awful, it can cause fainting. Through degeneration of its nose, it lost its sense of smell."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Smells so awful, it can cause fainting. Through degeneration of its nose, it lost its sense of smell."}],"evo":{"name":"grimer","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"muk","level":1,"min_level":38,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/89.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/89.png","capture":75,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"hp":1,"attack":1},"forms":[{"id":10113,"name":"muk-alola","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10113.png"}]}